extendedInfo.description: Ranbaxy Super Specialties presents for the 1st time in India - an Oncology Conference Planner android application. This application contains details of plenty of oncology conferences scheduled in 2013. It includes details like conference name, date, venue and website.You can also add your favourite CME/conference if it is missing from the list. A checklist is also provided which helps you to plan your conference in a better way (Registration, Stay and Travel). Notifications regarding your registration, stay and travel for the selected conferences (as favourites) will appear at regular intervals so that you plan everything well in advance.So, what are you waiting for ? Go grab it !! Install it now.Regards,Ranbaxy Super Specialties TeamSS/XTZ/AS/PG/LBL/02-73-311212
